high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the sink
Pick up a spoon from the end table
Move to the stove behind you
Put the spoon in a pot on the stove
Pick up the pot from the stove
Move to the table to the right of the stove
Place the pot on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon on the table to the right of the stove.

high_descs: Move forward, turn right, and go to the end table to the left of the counter.
Pick up the spoon on the end table, behind the salt.
Turn right, go forward, turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left to face the table with the toaster on it.
Place the pot on the table, to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small end table in the corner.
Pick up the spoon from the end table.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pan.
Pick the pan with the spoon up.
Turn right and walk near the toaster.
Put the pan on the right side of the toaster on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the pan and spoon to the right side of the toaster.
